CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FA North East patient has become the
OL,8,Ffirst teenager in the UK to have a
OL,9,Fpain-relieving implant fitted to his
OL,10,Fspinal cord to ease an agonising
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FThe pain was so bad that last year
OL,14,FRalph contemplated having his foot
OL,15,Famputated, having tried multiple
OL,16,Ftreatments including powerful pain
OL,17,Fkillers, physiotherapy and
OL,18,Fpsychological support.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
