OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FNow he has become the first teenager
OL,8,Fin the UK to have been fitted with a
OL,9,Fpioneering implant device at the
OL,10,FNewcastle's RVI Hospital to relieve
OL,11,Fhis condition.
OL,13,FIt uses spinal cord stimulation to
OL,14,Fdisrupt the signals travelling to the
OL,15,Fbrain in real time. A tiny battery
OL,16,Funder the skin provides a small
OL,17,Felectrical pulse to the spinal cord to
OL,18,Fblock the pain signals.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FExperts say it is a "closed loop,"
OL,8,Fmeaning it reacts to the patient's
OL,9,Fmovement, using the body's own signals
OL,10,Fto adapt and adjust the stimulation to
OL,11,Fmeet their needs.
OL,13,FCRPS happens when nerves incorrectly
OL,14,Fsend severe pain signals from the
OL,15,Faffected parts of the body. The
OL,16,Fimplants can be used for CRPS when
OL,17,Fother treatments have failed.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FAccording to Ralph, from the moment
OL,8,Fthe device was switched on after
OL,9,Fsurgery, his pain disappeared. He
OL,10,Fsaid: "For the first time in five
OL,11,Fyears, I'm pain free.
OL,13,F"My mum was emotional and so was I.
OL,14,FIt's not really hit me, I still can't
OL,15,Fget my head around it. I'm hoping the
OL,16,Fimplant is going to help me get my
OL,17,Flife back again.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,F"I couldn't plan before as I had to
OL,8,Fthink about how I would cope with
OL,9,Fpain. Now I am planning my future
OL,10,Fworking with cars and going on a road
OL,11,Ftrip with my family."
OL,13,FHis mother Tara Walton said: "It's
OL,14,Freally so special to see him smiling
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]uD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,F"Ralph has been through so much but
OL,8,Fthroughout he's had a great attitude,
OL,9,Fhe's continued to go to school,
OL,10,Fpushing himself further. He's been so
OL,11,Fdetermined to keep going, showing such
OL,12,Fresilience passing his GCSEs and going
OL,13,Fto college."
OL,15,FDr Sachin Rastogi, is an anaesthetist
OL,16,Fwho specialises in pain, and joined
OL,17,Fneurosurgeon Akbar Hussain to fit the
OL,18,Fimplant.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FDr Rastogi said the results of the
OL,8,Fprocedure were "immediate and
OL,9,Funprecedented".
OL,11,FHe said: "Seeing the impact of being
OL,12,Fpain-free for Ralph is simply one of
OL,13,Fthe most moving things I have
OL,14,Fexperienced in my career. This type of
OL,15,Fclosed-loop spinal cord stimulation
OL,16,Fhasn't been done in the UK before in
OL,17,Fan adolescent patient with this type
OL,18,Fof pain.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@NO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
