OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,F"The response has been so dramatic and
OL,8,Fthat is likely to do with his nervous
OL,9,Fsystem being young and highly
OL,10,Fadaptable."
OL,12,FMr Seed will continue rehabilitation
OL,13,Fto strengthen his foot, as well as
OL,14,Freceiving psychological support, and
OL,15,Fthe effect on his sleep and walking
OL,16,Fwill be monitored.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
