CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1784828906
OL,3,CNorth East teenager becomes country's
OL,4,Cyoungest person to receive spinal
OL,5,Cimplant
OL,7,FHe said: "We want other families who
OL,8,Fmay be going through chronic pain to
OL,9,Fknow about this condition and that
OL,10,Fthere is treatment for it. I'm so
OL,11,Fthankful to everyone for what they
OL,12,Fhave done for me."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
